{"tid":1550290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地 真係要有救人既覺悟 沙田又差少少","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:33:48.000Z","uid":200795,"like":174,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"d29e7f11e2cc2f5a05cc1adc2c88e6bd95a4325c","tid":1550290,"uid":200795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"沙田個班手足 你地齊齊衝埋去 果5-6個輕裝警犬一定唔夠打 一定救到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df80b00f0476a95e4e72b4150ff7252eb125b7da","tid":1550290,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64d95b109a00c7f63903d0d419cbef38711180bb","tid":1550290,"uid":200795,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"差少少 一擁而上一定救到 班狗淆到仆街"},{"pid":"bcb2c213d0f10c38354b7656b3eba43baa51ec6c","tid":1550290,"uid":62067,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"