ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"無勇武派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600192f3526bf120023f73734ef6581dbffbd99c","tid":1550290,"uid":111576,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"講真 打機有幾樣野一定要有覺悟<br />\n第一：救唔救人<br />\n第二：救人的話，人數比例相差夠唔夠大<br />\n第三：必定要有幾個死士，衝埋去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攬低距</span><br />\n第四：其他隊友一擁而上"},{"pid":"bb70b1c58ec19777ee31864ac7148f48c00fa3c8","tid":1550290,"uid":63838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"成堆CCTV影住又係難啲救嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd17e89e332a17504d73725f12b5fa1550b52721","tid":1550290,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"其實大家係上帝視角去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場班手足根本唔知現場情況<br />\n佢地唔知當時只係五個黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cf9d1e58d1ab410677857f9adeb75af2cb320c","tid":1550290,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"聽日唔玩激光唔玩火，一齊唱美國國歌感動美國國民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars,<br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched,<br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare,<br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night,<br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有呢首Hong Kong Anthem，香港國歌你唔係唔識唱下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港 Glory To Hong Kong》<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\nFor all of our tears on our land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\nDo you feel the rage in our cries?<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\nRise up and speak up! Our voice echoes<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\nFreedom shall shine upon us<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\nFor all of our fear that lingers<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\nWith faith, we shall never surrender<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\nWith blood, tears and sweat, we shall stride ahead<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\nFor this glory, lib-eral land<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\nWhen the stars no longer guide our path<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲<br />\nIn the fog, the horn of conscience summon us<br />\n&quot;捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n&ldquo;Persevere! For we are as one, with poise and be brave<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot;<br />\nCourage, wisdom, are long with us.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\nThe dawn has come. Let&rsquo;s revive our Hong Kong<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\nRevolution of our time! For righteousness!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\nDemocracy, n&rsquo;liberty, wish them long last here<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\nFor the glory of Hong Kong"},{"pid":"f72a90051d7d668dfe70db761ad216fa60cad14c","tid":1550290,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"193de9c185e729cb6b2a03daf86696728c623e73","tid":1550290,"uid":174502,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"2個幾月勇武冇進步過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal